                     <interp inst="t18160710-30-person252" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . On going to the prisoners house we found the hat lying on a chair.</p>

               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18160710-30-person253">
                  THOMAS 
                  THOMPSON
               <interp inst="t18160710-30-person253" type="surname" value="THOMPSON"></interp>
