                     <interp inst="t18160710-30-person253" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am an officer. On the 5th of June, between nine and ten at night, there came a knock at Mr. Newton's door, No. 56. St. John street, and the pocket book was thrown into the hall by some person with a note in it.</p>

               <p>(property produced and sworn to.)</p>

               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I kicked against something in the privy, and I found it was this hat, and so I took it.</p>

